Class TissueCCell

arcade.agent.cell.TissueCell

Direct Known Subclasses:
TissueSCell
public class TissueCCell
extends TissueHCell
Extension of TissueHCell for cancerous tissue cells.

TissueCCell agents are modified from their superclass:

  • Code change to CODE_C_CELL
  • If cell is quiescent, they may exit out of quiescence into neutral if there is space in their neighborhood
Since:
2.2
Version:

      public TissueCCell​(Simulation sim, int pop, Location loc, double vol, int age, java.util.Map<java.lang.String,​Parameter> params, MiniBox box)
      Creates a cancerous TissueCell agent given specific module versions.

      Changes the cell agent code to cancerous.

      Parameters:
      sim - the simulation instance
      pop - the population index
      loc - the location of the cell
      vol - the initial (and critical) volume of the cell
      age - the initial age of the cell in minutes
      params - the map of parameter name to Parameter objects
      box - the map of module name to version
